metadata.description:
Natureâ€¦ the first giver. Everything that arises from the Earth has something to give, asking not much in return.



Every tree has a story to tell. Every leaf has a song to sing. Every flower has a beauty to show. 



But only for those who are capable of giving an ear. 



Welcome to the Arboretum of Opulence, the refuge of those who are aware of nature is a true source of inspiration, a channel to tell stories never heard before.
